node.title: Two charged with murder of Gisborne woman Maraea Smith
node.description: Two people have been charged with the murder of a Gisborne woman nearly three weeks ago.
node.content:
["Two people have been charged with the murder of a Gisborne woman nearly three weeks ago.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Maraea Smith died on her 36th birthday after being shot in Tair\u0101whiti.", "A man, 36, and a woman, 30, were arrested today in Manurewa, Auckland, and charged with her murder.", "They appeared in the Manukau District Court and were remanded in custody.", "They will next appear before a judge in the High Court at Gisborne on 6 May 2022."]
